                <note rend="inline" type="source">881.512/26: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Diplomatic Agent and Consul General at Tangier</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Denning</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-04-21T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 21, 1923—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>11. Agency’s despatch no. 117 of March 23.</p>
                <p>Is it your opinion that the collection of the consumption tax would affect
                    American citizens more unfavorably than it would the nationals of the most
                    favored nation? Reply by cable.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
